snippet.title: Duet Steam Release - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Duet is a hypnotic arcade action game with a mesmerizingly beautiful soundtrack by Melbourne composer and Gotye multi-instrumentalist Tim Shiel.

Now available on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/292600

Download on the App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/duet/id634235735?at=11lt4d&ct=youtube

Get it on Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kumobius.android.duet
